item.title: CVE-2023-35126|2023-10-19T16:02:29.998Z -- ichitaro%202023 -- ichitaro%202023
item.description: An out-of-bounds write vulnerability exists within the parsers for both the "DocumentViewStyles" and "DocumentEditStyles" streams of Ichitaro 2023 1.0.1.59372 when processing types 0x0000-0x0009 of a style record with the type 0x2008. A specially crafted document can cause memory corruption, which can lead to arbitrary code execution. An attacker can provide a malicious file to trigger this vulnerability.
